	"description": "Individual scraping jobs within a squid that need to be executed. Contains specific parameters, URLs, and settings for a single scraping operation.\n\n**Note:** The accepted task input keys (e.g., `url`, `city`, `activity`) depend on the crawler used in your squid.\n\nTo view the valid keys for your crawler, refer to the [Get crawler parameters](#f0170945-174a-433b-b24d-b35731e78f4e) endpoint.\n\nOnly the keys listed under the `\"task\"` object are valid for this endpoint."
